<strong>新界西</strong><br />\n元朗：68X                        [元州邨]<br />\n天水圍：69X, 265B         [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(大興)：66X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(虎地)：67X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(新墟)：67X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(市中心)：60X         [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(良田)：58X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門碼頭：59X                [元州邨]<br />\n深井：52X                        [元州邨]<br />\n荃灣：30X, 33A, 234X    [元州邨]<br />\n梨木樹：36A                   [東京街西]<br />\n海濱花園：238X             [元州邨]<br />\n石籬：32                          [麗蘿樓]<br />\n葵涌：33A, 37                 [元州邨]<br />\n葵涌：36A                       [東京街西]<br />\n青衣：41                          [元州邨]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>❗️正門位於通州街(天橋底)，有升降機<br />\n❗️側門位於英華街，有扶手電梯<br />\n<br />\n交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"10524af728734f622b1f0101b884fd5e47fc3ee2","tid":2046473,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04a6f1312703677dda9781782f3ef8e3cd37a0b0","tid":2046473,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e32b305f92e9aa551bcc1049aae5de888e0caa3","tid":2046473,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"【保釋及送車位置】<br />\n<br />\n✵送車位位於法院停車場🅿️<br />\n✵揾唔到就圍住法院兜一圈⭕️<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《區 域 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉右再轉右行幾級樓梯，兜到去消防局停車場<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《東 區 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（巴士站對面）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《九 龍 城 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門／其他秘道<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：行去送車位既通道有間房仔<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（小馬路）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《觀 塘 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（馬路燈前轉）／正門轉右再轉右（見到郵政局轉）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《沙 田 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（公園隔嚟）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《屯 門 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左（送車口好細）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《西 九 龍 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：法院範圍內扶手電梯／法院範圍小額錢債處門口<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：法院範圍內扶手電梯／法院範圍小額錢債處門口<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左直行到渠務署污水房（地盤對面）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"1a6ab4fc76263daa5c37a5b842e391b78d902e80","tid":2046473,"uid":34056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c673d0dd7dddbd4907453d97838f4fc8b9cd37d","tid":2046473,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a6f1312703677dda9781782f3ef8e3cd37a0b0","tid":2046473,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"有新案件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fecf93cbc139fca688891bf04183603640e69ad","tid":2046473,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b882f7bca656677430762eea3a5b2daa242baba","tid":2046473,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"法庭繼續要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass